- Consistent with the fintech aesthetic: premium, calm, data-forward
- Serif display typography for hero headings; sans-serif for body
- Wide hero with centered content; generous padding; 12-column grid impression
- Cards with border radii 16–20px, shadows 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
- Primary green actions (#2f6f63); secondary teal/gray-teal (#2b6250)
- Background and surfaces: Hero Beige (#f3efe6), Page Taupe (#a79e96), Neutral White (#ffffff)
- Typography: Playfair Display or Georgia for headings; Inter or Roboto for body
- Clear visual hierarchy: hero heading, subheading, search/filters, action buttons

